Package: BioClockR
Title: Clinical Biological Age Estimator Using NHANES Public Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Naresh", "Gumala", email = "nareshgumala123@github.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Estimates biological age from routine clinical biomarkers using the
    PhenoAge formula (Levine et al. 2018). Validated against NHANES 2015-2020
    public data and NCHS linked mortality files. Includes a Shiny app for
    interactive biological age estimation.
